=== Pronunciation ===
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /smεl/

=== Noun ===
'''smell''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[smells]])

# (''Uncountable'') The [[sense]] that detects certain [[substance]]s in the air by means of the [[nose]]
#:''Dogs have a keen sense of smell''.
# (''Countable'') The scent given off by something.
#:''I love the smell of fresh bread''!

====Synonyms====
*[[aroma]] (2)
*[[odour]] (2)
*[[scent]] (2)

